## 👋 About Me

Hello, I'm **Devi Sai Prasanna**, a third-year Computer Science Engineering student with a passion for software development, artificial intelligence, and continuous learning.

I believe the best way to learn is by building, experimenting, and solving real-world problems. Through academic projects, self-learning, and hands-on development, I have developed a strong interest in creating technology solutions that make a meaningful impact.

My goal is to grow as a software engineer while continuously expanding my knowledge of emerging technologies and industry best practices.

